title: ISL: FC Goa beat Kerala Blasters, take top spot
text: 23 Oct 2015Frenchman Gregory Arnolin's 84th minute strike helped FC Goa edge past Kerala Blasters FC 2-1 in a keenly contested ISL football game and take top spot in the league table in Margao in Goa yesterday. Into the final minutes and the game tied at 1-1, central defender Gregory, who is a French professional, made it count to score the winner much to the delight of the home fans at the Jawaharlal Nehru Stadium, Fatorda.
